  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This is the <strong>first </strong></i><strong>entry</strong> <i>of a <strong>three-part </strong></i>horror <i>series </i>that blends<i> </i><strong>exploration</strong>, <strong>escape-room challenges</strong>, and <strong>stealth-based survival </strong>elements<i>. </i>This part includes <strong>three chapters</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/2b47d88d78341f535b95f646d2ae61f2.poster.avif?t=1773708382\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/2b47d88d78341f535b95f646d2ae61f2.webm?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/2b47d88d78341f535b95f646d2ae61f2.mp4?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are John Rand, a search-and-rescue officer stationed in Richburg National Park. When young Elena Peterson disappears during a family hike, John and his team are dispatched to find her. During the search, John becomes separated from the others, forced to retrace his steps alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/c7561e224c0553cf5064d0758c52acc3.poster.avif?t=1773708382\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/c7561e224c0553cf5064d0758c52acc3.webm?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/c7561e224c0553cf5064d0758c52acc3.mp4?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam Achievements:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/15af9f41369b4a9d3513a3f10c320eec.avif?t=1773708382\" width=1162 height=844 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chapters in Part 1</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chapter 1</strong>: Connecting the dots.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Chapter 2</strong>: Breath of fresh air.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Chapter 3</strong>: Back to square one. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes in Part 1</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Standard</strong> - classic game run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Torture</strong> - replay Chapter 3 with a more challenging puzzle (unlocked once Standard mode is completed).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun</strong> - replay the game with a timer, no cut scenes (unlocked once Standard mode is completed).</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This is the <strong>first </strong></i><strong>entry</strong> <i>of a <strong>three-part </strong></i>horror <i>series </i>that blends<i> </i><strong>exploration</strong>, <strong>escape-room challenges</strong>, and <strong>stealth-based survival </strong>elements<i>. </i>This part includes <strong>three chapters</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/2b47d88d78341f535b95f646d2ae61f2.poster.avif?t=1773708382\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/2b47d88d78341f535b95f646d2ae61f2.webm?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/2b47d88d78341f535b95f646d2ae61f2.mp4?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are John Rand, a search-and-rescue officer stationed in Richburg National Park. When young Elena Peterson disappears during a family hike, John and his team are dispatched to find her. During the search, John becomes separated from the others, forced to retrace his steps alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/c7561e224c0553cf5064d0758c52acc3.poster.avif?t=1773708382\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/c7561e224c0553cf5064d0758c52acc3.webm?t=1773708382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809570/extras/c75